<Para>
<Text>Reg. 33(2) substituted (26.11.2014) by <Citation id="rnb8sic5-d3e45612a1310" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/2887" Class="UnitedKingdomStatutoryInstrument" Year="2014" Number="2887" Title="The Universal Credit (Digital Service) Amendment Regulations 2014">The Universal Credit (Digital Service) Amendment Regulations 2014 (S.I. 2014/2887)</Citation>, <CitationSubRef id="rnb8sic5-d3e45615a1310" CitationRef="rnb8sic5-d3e45612a1310" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/2887/regulation/1" SectionRef="regulation-1">regs. 1</CitationSubRef>, <CitationSubRef id="rnb8sic5-d3e45618a1310" CitationRef="rnb8sic5-d3e45612a1310" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/2887/regulation/2/2/c" SectionRef="regulation-2-2-c" Operative="true">2(2)(c)</CitationSubRef> (with <CitationSubRef id="rnb8sic5-d3e45621a1310" CitationRef="rnb8sic5-d3e45612a1310" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/2887/regulation/5" SectionRef="regulation-5">reg. 5</CitationSubRef>)</Text>
